once you start the program click on file open to find the txt doc and make sure you save the text doc in the program folder, so it wont crash.
when adding words make sure to enter ADD with a space and if with multiple words put a comma, for example: ADD jump(V),run(V),...
If you want to add a verb put (V) at the end of each word, if noun add (N).
To stop adding word Enter stop with a space.
If you click on the display menu bar you can select verb or nouns that sorted on the right and unsorted on the left.

Text doc should be like this
Jump(V)
RUN(V)
apple(N)
